Plans for 0.2.0
===============

  W = Work in progress
  D = Done
  P = Postponed
  ? = Questionable

  [W] Implement spell-checking using PyEnchant
        [D] Script to test PyEnchant installation
        [D] Outline general spell-checking strategy
        [D] Glade files for dialogs (Gedit!)
        [D] lib: langlib
        [D] gui: config entries
        [ ] gui: Spell check dialog (wxSpellCheckerDialog.py!)
        [ ] gui: Settings dialog
        [ ] gui: delegate
        [D] gui: Menu entry visibility
        [ ] Test error handling
        [ ] Ensure that PyEnchant is easily installable.
  [?] Revise terminology: project = main document + translation document
  [ ] Update Finnish translation


